title: On debate night, Trump gets out-tweeted by a GOP rival
text: There was high anticipation for Donald Trump's running commentary on the first Democratic debate. But the bombastic Republican front-runner ended up only sending out a few tweets of his own throughout the night. And the tone was rather... well, sedate.
